WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:07.866
Mrs. Lu is sick

2
00:00:07.866 --> 00:00:09.266
Why don't you go back first?

3
00:00:09.266 --> 00:00:10.566
If there is anything, I will pass it on for you first.

4
00:00:10.566 --> 00:00:12.666
When he is well, he will definitely find you first.

5
00:00:12.666 --> 00:00:13.866
Mr. Lu is sick

6
00:00:13.866 --> 00:00:15.300
Why can't I look at him?

7
00:00:15.533 --> 00:00:16.866
Is it an infectious disease?

8
00:00:20.133 --> 00:00:20.933
Lu Chaoyue

9
00:00:24.666 --> 00:00:25.933
What nonsense did you just say?

10
00:00:25.933 --> 00:00:27.633
How could I have an infectious disease?

11
00:00:30.666 --> 00:00:33.300
What's the matter? Are you in some trouble?

12
00:00:33.300 --> 00:00:35.200
Bye. What's going on?

13
00:00:35.200 --> 00:00:36.866
What did I do wrong again?

14
00:00:37.400 --> 00:00:39.266
Is there anyone who dares to bully you?

15
00:00:39.933 --> 00:00:42.333
Who dares to bully me except you?

16
00:00:42.333 --> 00:00:43.766
Then tell me where I went wrong.

17
00:00:43.766 --> 00:00:44.900
Can I change it?

18
00:00:46.766 --> 00:00:49.166
Manman, why are you crying?

19
00:00:51.900 --> 00:00:53.066
It's all my fault manman

20
00:00:53.566 --> 00:00:55.600
Then you hit me you hit me

21
00:00:58.166 --> 00:00:59.900
Who told you not to tell me?

22
00:00:59.966 --> 00:01:02.366
It's you who protected my father's good son for me

23
00:01:02.533 --> 00:01:04.300
Do you think that's noble?

